<li>"William Leggett, Spokesman of Jacksonian Democracy," <i>Political Science Quarterly</i> Vol. 58, No. 4 (Dec., 1943), pp. 581-594 <a href="http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0032-3195%28194312%2958%3A4%3C581%3AWLSOJD%3E2.0.CO%3B2-R" class="external text" title="http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0032-3195%28194312%2958%3A4%3C581%3AWLSOJD%3E2.0.CO%3B2-R" rel="nofollow">JSTOR</a></li>
