<li>"Beard and the Constitution: The History of an Idea," <i>American Quarterly</i> Vol. 2, No. 3 (Autumn, 1950), pp. 195-213 <a href="http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0003-0678%28195023%292%3A3%3C195%3ABATCTH%3E2.0.CO%3B2-F" class="external text" title="http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0003-0678%28195023%292%3A3%3C195%3ABATCTH%3E2.0.CO%3B2-F" rel="nofollow">JSTOR</a></li>
